# ⚡ Important Interview Concepts

### 1️⃣ What is Time Travel?

Allows querying historical data within retention period.

### 2️⃣ What is Fail-safe?

Additional 7 days after Time Travel.
❌ Not accessible by users.
Only Snowflake support.

### 3️⃣ Does Time Travel Increase Storage?

Yes — Snowflake stores micro-partition versions.

### 4️⃣ Can We Time Travel Schema & Database?

✅ Yes

Example:

```sql
UNDROP DATABASE FOOD_DISTRIBUTION_DB;
```

